1 incurred by the office of the Administrator of Credit Unions in carrying out its supervisory and
2 auditing functions.
3 (c) All revenue derived from fees will be placed into a special account to be administered
4 solely for the operation of the Credit Union Division.
5 (d) The Administrator may waive any fee, in whole or in part, for any credit union or
